    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that shows beautifully inside and out. The exterior presents extremely well with a clean, well-kept finish, the interior is outstanding and appears very lightly worn, and the car runs and drives exactly as it should. This is the kind of car that has clearly been cared for, and a buyer can expect a standout example that needs nothing beyond normal ownership and enjoyment.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "Used car in fair condition. It runs and drives and appears to be a usable vehicle, but it shows noticeable wear from age and use. Expect cosmetic imperfections and some items that may need attention, though it is not in rough project-car shape. Overall, it is a decent budget-friendly option for someone who wants a functional vehicle without expecting excellent condition.",
      "price": 16900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price. It shows age and wear consistent with an inexpensive pre-owned vehicle, making it a practical choice for a commuter, first-time driver, or buyer looking for a solid project with real potential. Priced to move and presented with transparency, this is a sensible opportunity to get behind the wheel without overspending.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner with good bones and lots of potential for someone who wants a practical daily, a first car, or a weekend project. It shows its age and has the usual wear you\u2019d expect, but it still offers solid value for the money and a chance to get into a car without breaking the bank. If you appreciate a straightforward deal and don\u2019t mind a vehicle with a bit of character, this one could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget driver with a solid, mechanical feel and the kind of straightforward platform enthusiasts like to sort and improve. The engine pulls through the rev range, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis has the usable, planted character of a car that has not been overcomplicated. Cosmetic wear and age are present, but that is reflected in the price. A great candidate for someone wanting an affordable entry point, a dependable runabout with character, or a platform to refresh over time. Priced to move while still recognizing its usable condition and enthusiast appeal.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Used and rough around the edges, but ready to go. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with honest character and plenty of story left to tell, this ride has the kind of lived-in charm that makes every trip feel a little more memorable. It\u2019s an affordable way to get behind the wheel of something with presence, personality, and real potential for someone who appreciates a diamond-in-the-rough. Whether you need a budget-friendly set of wheels, a practical backup, or a project with soul, this one offers a chance to own it without stretching your wallet.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and would best suit a buyer seeking an inexpensive daily driver, starter vehicle, or practical project. A straightforward opportunity to own a usable vehicle without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
